      "content": {
        "summary": "Ontario corporations maintain corporate records, including articles, by-laws, minutes/resolutions, securities registers, and significant-control information.",
        "tooltip": "Use this citation track for Ontario minute-book completeness, securities register support, beneficial-ownership review, and registered/head-office record storage.",
